strings: <voice_0x01000C44><se_def>Awesome!: yes, sir! I hope you are having a good time.
<voice_0x01000C45><se_def>Awesome!: King Ted explained us everything. Sorry for confusing you
<voice_0x01000C46><se_def>Awesome!: Domagus is the real villain. Stop those evil clowns!
<voice_0x01000C47><se_def>Awesome!: But now I can't let go. As the new leader, I still have a lot to do. I must lead people here.
<voice_0x01000C49><se_def>Awesome!: King Trudeau says you are looking for Dormago.
<voice_0x01000C4A><se_def>Awesome!: Here are some tips. Ask my brother Angel to accompany you on your quest.
<voice_0x01000C4B><se_def>China: Youkai Youkai Didn't I tell you not to break the rules?
<voice_0x01000C4C><se_def>Awesome!: I can't tell! I don't tell you!
<voice_0x01000C4D><se_def>Awesome!: Now you're just here, and we're fine without you.
<voice_0x01000C4F><se_def>Awesome!: Here everyone has an obligation to follow it. If there is no liability
<voice_0x01000C50><se_def>China: ......that means I'm mad! In spite of the bushes.
<voice_0x01000C52><se_def>China: You are very clear. with ava i wanna go with the boys. I will do anything to avenge the abbot's death.
<voice_0x01000C53><se_low>King of tricks: I waited in the car with Mediah...
<voice_0x01000C54><se_def>Awesome!: Well! I trust in Angelo's care and wish you a safe trip.
